      "side": 1,
      "message": "This really isn\u0027t intended to be used this way. RS_TRIPLE_CFLAGS is something that is RenderScript-specific. I need to look more closely at what is happening here, but it seems like you are missing the actual specification of a proper triple, or those defines would already be present for you. Why can\u0027t you generate the files and use the traditional C/CPP build rules?",
      "range": {
